title: [Vornavis, Peasant Holdings]
description: Smoke curls lazily from the chimney of a peasant cottage, its whitewashed walls almost lost beneath the overhang of golden thatch.  A matching shed and storage bin huddle close by with the common tracks between them worn to bare dirt.  A well-worn path leads north towards the river road.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, southeast, south, southwest, west, northwest
